SELECT id, 
"role", 
client_id,
created_at - interval '8 hour'  as created_at, 
updated_at - interval '8 hour'  as updated_at ,
deleted_at - interval '8 hour'  as deleted_at 
from public."Project_Team_Roles"  
WHERE created_at - interval '8 hour 2 second'>  (@{activity('Lookup_Project_Team_Roles_MaxDate').output.firstRow.max_created_at}) 
OR updated_at - interval '8 hour 2 second'> (@{activity('Lookup_Project_Team_Roles_MaxDate').output.firstRow.max_updated_at})

SELECT id, client_id, "type", "name",
created_at - interval '8 hour'  as created_at, 
updated_at - interval '8 hour'  as updated_at,
deleted_at - interval '8 hour'  as deleted_at 
from public."Cost_Drivers_Optimizers" 
WHERE created_at - interval '8 hour 2 second'>  (@{activity('Lookup_Cost_Drivers_Optimizers_MaxDate').output.firstRow.max_created_at})
OR updated_at - interval '8 hour 2 second'> (@{activity('Lookup_Cost_Drivers_Optimizers_MaxDate').output.firstRow.max_updated_at})

source.sqlReaderQuery:
SELECT 
CASE WHEN max_created_at IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT('''',CONVERT(varchar(50), max_created_at),'''')
ELSE '''1990-01-01''' END as max_created_at,
CASE WHEN max_updated_at IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT('''',CONVERT(varchar(50), max_updated_at),'''')
ELSE '''1990-01-01''' END as max_updated_at
 FROM(SELECT MAX(FORMAT(created_at,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')) as max_created_at,  
				MAX(FORMAT(updated_at,'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')) as max_updated_at 
		FROM dbo."Project_Team_Roles") a
